rows.label: tlk000501_05_msg0001
rows.name:
This is secret base. Nilny use this
place often.

rows.label: tlk000501_05_msg0002
rows.name:
As agent of Special Distribution Audit
Bureau, have been seeking evidence of
Bahn's misdeeds for past several years.

rows.label: tlk000501_05_msg0003
rows.name:
Thought artificial Blade case would be
final nail in coffin for our Chairman.

rows.label: tlk000501_05_msg0004
rows.name:
But he slip away again, and we still not
manage to arrest him.

rows.label: tlk000501_05_msg0005
rows.name:
Biggest priority is to find place of
hiding.
